description: Oregon's Sabrina Ionescu drives against California's Mikayla Cowling (3) and Kristine Anigwe (31) NCAA college basketball game in Eugene, Ore., Friday, Feb. 2, 2018. Ionescu scored 28 points as Oregon won 91-54. (Brian Davies/The Register-Guard via AP)
